Aqua-Echo-Privacy-Policy

Thank you for choosing AquaEcho, your personal water reminder app dedicated to helping you stay hydrated. 
This Privacy Policy outlines how we collect and use your information to provide you with a seamless experience. By using AquaEcho, you agree to the practices described in this policy.

1. Information We Collect: 

1.1 Usernames:
- AquaEcho collects and stores the username you provide during the onboarding process. Once set, the username cannot be edited. This information is used to personalize your experience within the app.
  
1.2 Notification Permissions:
- To send you daily hydration reminders, AquaEcho requires your explicit permission to send local notifications.

2. How We Use Your Information:

2.1 Usernames:
- Your username is used to personalize your water reminder messages and enhance your overall experience with AquaEcho.

2.2 Notification Permissions:
- The notification permission you grant is solely used to send local daily reminders for staying hydrated. No other information related to notifications is accessed or stored.

3. Data Security:
- At AquaEcho, we prioritize the security and privacy of your information. Our app is designed to provide you with a personalized experience without collecting or storing any user data.
The username you provide is used solely within the app to enhance your experience, such as addressing you by your name in notifications. We do not store, share, or transmit any personal information, ensuring the confidentiality and integrity of your data.
Rest assured, your privacy is of utmost importance to us, and we take industry-standard measures to safeguard the limited information we handle for an optimal user experience.
  
4. User Controls:

4.1 Usernames:
- Once a username is set, it cannot be edited. If you encounter any issues or wish to change your username for a specific reason, please contact our support team at [support@nquila-dev.com].

5. Updates and Amendments:
- AquaEcho reserves the right to update or amend this Privacy Policy periodically. Significant changes will be communicated within the app or through email.

6. Contact Us:
- If you have any questions or concerns about this Privacy Policy, please reach out to us at [support@nquila-dev.com].
By using AquaEcho, you acknowledge that you have read and understood this Privacy Policy and agree to its terms. Stay hydrated!

